\section{Summarising one run attempt}

The CLI needs more context than just the updated run record.  It needs to
know whether the command actually launched shells, whether the tutorial
was already complete, and whether the latest step blocked further
progress.

<<classes>>=
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class RunResult:
    """Summary of a tutorial execution attempt."""

    tutorial: Tutorial
    run: TutorialRun
    progress: ProgressState
    executed_steps: int
    restarted: bool = False
    already_finished: bool = False
    blocked_step: TutorialStep | None = None
    blocked_transcript: StepTranscript | None = None
@

