\section{Detecting tutorial changes across resumes}

Resuming a run against a different tutorial file would be confusing at
best and misleading at worst.  We therefore compare the saved source
digest against the current tutorial digest before resuming an unfinished
run.

<<functions>>=
def ensure_run_matches_tutorial(tutorial: Tutorial, run: TutorialRun) -> None:
    """Reject resuming a run if the tutorial file changed."""

    if run.tutorial_source_digest is None or tutorial.source_digest is None:
        return
    if run.tutorial_source_digest != tutorial.source_digest:
        raise RuntimeError(
            f"Tutorial {tutorial.id!r} changed since this run began. "
            "Use --restart to begin a fresh run."
        )
@
